title: Dhol
subTitle: Four lazy friends want to make easy money and aim to marry a rich girl. Their plan backfires after they meet Ritu and get embroiled with a dangerous criminal.

title: Kaalia
subTitle: Kallu's life changes after his brother, Shamu, meets with an accident and requires money for his treatment. As a result, he is forced to rob Shamu's employer but gets arrested instead.

title: Bal Ganesh 3
subTitle: Dhoti, Topi and Suit Boot are more than happy to oblige when a group of alien kids come over to listen to adventure stories about their favourite Bal Ganesh.

title: Mann
subTitle: Dev and Priya fall in love despite being engaged to their respective partners and decide to reunite after six months to get married. However, destiny has other plans for them.

title: Bandhan
subTitle: Thakur marries his mistress when his first wife, Pooja, is unable to bear children. His brother-in-law opposes this marriage to save the dignity of his sister and fights to reunite them.

title: Darr
subTitle: Swept up in a whirlwind of fear and romance, Kiran teeters on the edge of a mental and emotional precipice. While Sunil keeps holding on to her, Rahul spares no effort to drag her down with himself.

title: Raghuveer
subTitle: Ravi, an honest policeman, leads the bodyguard team of the chief minister. When his college-going brother, Raghuveer, is arrested and jailed, Ravi breaks all ties with him out of embarrassment.

title: Hungama
subTitle: A millionaire businessman living in a village decides to move to the city with his wife. However, things take a comical turn as a case of mistaken identity causes chaos in their lives.

title: Elaan
subTitle: A.C.P. Ramakant Chaudhary, an uptight police officer, struggles with bringing his elder son's killers to justice. Vishal, his younger son, decides to take matters in his own hands.

title: Elaan
subTitle: A.C.P. Ramakant Chaudhary, an uptight police officer, struggles with bringing his elder son's killers to justice. Vishal, his younger son, decides to take matters in his own hands.

title: Aakhri Adalat
subTitle: An honest police officer decides to take the law into his own hands when he loses his job, and the thugs he caught get released due to some technicality.

title: Jurmana
subTitle: A flambouyant businessman places a bet with his former college friend to woo their professor's young daughter. However, the bet leads to a series of unexpected consequences.

title: Jai Dakshineshwar Kali Maa
subTitle: A young woman is harassed and tormented by her mother-in-law. She is rescued from her predicament by the Goddess Kali who is pleased with her ardent devotion.

title: Hadh Kar Di Aapne
subTitle: Raj, a detective, goes on a Europe trip to investigate his friend's case. There, he falls in love with Anjali, who is impersonating her best friend.

title: Dilwale Dulhania Le Jayenge
subTitle: While travelling across Europe, Raj and Simran unexpectedly grow close, only to be separated by family expectations, prompting Raj to fight for love and tradition.

title: Hum Aapke Dil Mein Rehte Hain
subTitle: Love begins with a marriage of convenience and stays with Megha and Vijay in the throes of separation. In a classic case of unfortunate timing, one realises it too soon, while the other is too late.

title: Baghban
subTitle: Raj and Pooja live an upsetting life when their sons refuse to reciprocate their affections and take care of them.

title: Anth
subTitle: Kali, the son of a gangster, rapes and kills Pooja, and frames her fiance, who is killed in custody, for the crime. As a result, her brother, Vijay, vows revenge against Kali.

title: Anth

title: Zulm Ka Badla
subTitle: Verma adopts Geeta, the orphaned daughter of his friend, who grows up to marry his son, Anil. However, when a gangster dies during Anil's probe, both men suspect that Geeta is responsible.

title: Bahurani
subTitle: Amit wants to marry a modern woman but his parents get him married to a village girl, Madhuri. When Amit refuses to accept her as his wife, Madhuri reinvents herself as Malathi and re-enters his life.

title: Daata
subTitle: A decorated school teacher's life is upended by devastating rumours, which ultimately leads to his death. His son Kundan now seeks vengeance.

title: Gundaraj
subTitle: Ajay and Pooja fall in love and decide to get married. To earn money and get settled, Ajay applies for a job in Bombay, but is framed in a rape case and is imprisoned for four years.

title: Gumrah
subTitle: Seeing Roshni's talent for singing, Rahul gives her a break and they eventually fall in love. On a foreign trip, she is arrested for possession of cocaine, not knowing that it is all Rahul's doing.

title: Vinashak
subTitle: A diligent and determined police officer is tasked with uncovering the truth behind a crooked warden involved in illicit weapon trafficking.

title: Itihaas
subTitle: Naina, who is betrothed to an influential man, falls in love and elopes with Karan, the son of an employee of her fiance. Soon, bounty hunters start hunting the duo to claim a hefty reward.

title: Gupt
subTitle: After his stepfather is murdered, Sahil gets arrested but he manages to escape prison to prove his innocence. However, Inspector Udham Singh sets off to capture him.
